translations.translation:
{You cannot perceive it with your eyes}

This means that you cannot surround it because it is too delicate to be grasped.,
How can you understand it when it does not understand itself, which is light from it?! {And He grasps the eyesights} to envelop everything with His knowledge and the ease of His understanding {There has come to you enlightenment from your Lord} i.e. clear verses, they are the manifestations of His attributes which are the lights of the hearts' eyesights.
